    "### 2.d Sensitivity of HRP weights — clustering vs. allocation traversal\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "70b63365",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-05-02T16:20:39.989750Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-05-02T16:20:39.989697Z",
